Package universitysystem.entity

Class Teacher

java.lang.Object
universitysystem.entity.User
universitysystem.entity.Employee
universitysystem.entity.Teacher
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<User>, CanCreate, CanLogin, Runnable, Scheduling, StudentsInfo, Subscription
public class Teacher extends Employee implements StudentsInfo, Scheduling
Class Teacher in the university system. A teacher is a faculty member invited by the university to conduct courses, evaluate students and monitor their academic performance.

It features a menu-driven interface for the teacher to execute various grading tasks, such as entering regular marks, assigning final exam grades, viewing student information, and addressing complaints.
